SAMPLE RUN:

INPUT: Poppie Panther 3045
OUTPUT: PanthP45

===========================================================
DESIGN:

a) Inputs

firstName - string
lastName - string
fourDigits -int



-----------------------------------------------------------
b) Outputs

userName - string

-----------------------------------------------------------
c) Calculations

fourDigits % 100 = last 2 digits

-----------------------------------------------------------
d) Pseudocode

DECLARE firstName string
DECLARE lastName string
DECLARE fourDigits int
DECLARE userName string
DISPLAY Welcome message and prompt
INPUT firstName
INPUT lastName
INPUT fourDIgits
IF lastName len < 5
  pass
ELSE
  lastName = lastName.substr(0, 5)
userName = lastName + firstName.substr(0, 1) + to_string(fourDigits % 100)
DISPLAY username with exit message